template(name="robusto")
  .grid
    .column
      +siteInfo site=site descriptionTemplate=descriptionTemplate

      .block
        img.zoom(src='/images/robusto_2_1000w.png')
        .icon-bg
          i.fa.fa-search-plus.fa-lg
        figcaption
          h5 The data visualization view.
          p Several graphing options were offered, including building a date filter widget that doubled as a histogram of results.

    .column
      .block
        img.zoom(src='/images/robusto_1_1000w.png')
        .icon-bg
          i.fa.fa-search-plus.fa-lg
        figcaption
          h5 The hand-filter view.
          p Hands could be filtered by a number of criteria, such as player name, booleans on stat fields and date ranges.

      .block
        img.zoom(src='/images/robusto_parser.png')
        .icon-bg
          i.fa.fa-search-plus.fa-lg
        figcaption
          h5 A sampling of code from the hand history parser.
          p This was extracted and open-sourced as a gem called "Parsley". 